### REGISTRO DE USUÁRIO
POST http://localhost:5000/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "claudia@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### LOGIN
POST http://localhost:5000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "claudia@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

# Copie o access_token retornado e substitua na linha Authorization abaixo

###

### BUSCAR LIVROS NA API DO GOOGLE BOOKS
GET http://localhost:5000/api/user/books/search?query=grandes+esperancas
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

###

### ADICIONAR LIVRO COM REVIEW
POST http://localhost:5000/api/user/books/0CgREQAAQBAJ
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Excelente leitura, recomendo muito!",
  "status": "lendo"
}

###

### ATUALIZAR REVIEW DE UM LIVRO (PUT)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/user/books/0CgREQAAQBAJ
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

{
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "Gostei muito, mas prefiro outros do Dickens",
  "status": "lido"
}

###

### ATUALIZAR SOMENTE O STATUS (PATCH)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/user/books/0CgREQAAQBAJ/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

{
  "status": "lido"
}

###

### DELETAR UM LIVRO DO USUÁRIO
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/user/books/0CgREQAAQBAJ
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}
